{"tid":647192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［絲入］sex感覺喺點？男女邊嗰舒服啲？我想分享","createTime":"2018-04-29T16:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T12:02:54.000Z","uid":177135,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7f72dabe582ddb8d0604629c9016713dfd31f3ab","tid":647192,"uid":177135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想分享下...<br />\n<br />\n本人拍拖2次 性經驗尚淺<br />\n第1個因爲性觀念不夾 所以分開<br />\n佢希望留個處比老公 但佢無當我係佢以後既老公 拍拖兩年 乜都唔比摸 唔會含 唔會用手幫<br />\n我自己又好有需要 唔想對佢唔住 自己知無信心等到結婚先啪 忍得太痛苦 所以忍痛放手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第2個女友 性觀念又喺比較守舊 <br />\n佢好驚比人知有性生活 會扮處女 打死唔認啪過<br />\n不過梗喺無之前嗰個咁守舊 所以相處很好<br />\n但佢成日都覺得男女扑野<br />\n喺男方舒服過女方N倍<br />\n所以次次都話喺因爲我想做 佢先做<br />\n佢次次做完都話：舒服啦？開心啦？<br />\n講到自己完全無享受咁 我有點介意<br />\n不過我完全唔覺囉 我幫佢舔 同佢啪 <br />\n佢明明勁享受 點解又唔認呢？<br />\n<br />\n所以想問問絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地啪喺咩感覺？真喺無feel?<br />\n喺咪男會舒服過女好多？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fef7e0b1709aba97d03f5eddf987882b6398b4","tid":647192,"uid":21423,"like":20,"dislike":8,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e78ab0bc2e55568f114f67c0c5b85ee41472ee0e","tid":647192,"uid":177135,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0fef7e0b1709aba97d03f5eddf987882b6398b4","tid":647192,"uid":21423,"like":20,"dislike":8,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:08:52.000Z","msg":"唔明 如果用錯左 好對唔住<img src=\"/assets/fa